# Metric Resource: InformationContent
<https://w3id.org/soel/metric/InformationContent> a dqv:Metric ;

    dcterms:identifier "https://w3id.org/soel/metric/InformationContent" ;
    dcterms:title "Semantic-level comparison using WordNet synsets and IC scores"@en ;
    rdfs:label "InformationContent: Semantic-level comparison using WordNet synsets and IC scores"^^xsd:string ;
    vivo:abbreviation "IC"^^xsd:string ;
    dcat:version "0.0.1"^^xsd:string ;
    ftr:status "Active"@en ;
    dcat:landingPage <https://w3id.org/soel/metric/InformationContent> ;

    # Descriptive Content
    dcterms:description """
This metric aims to evaluate the similarity between generated label and the labels in the gold standard ontology with focus of semantic-level comparison using WordNet synsets.

**Calculation Process:**

1. Map the generated label to WordNet synsets.

2. Choose a information content source corpus (eg. SemCor, Brown, BNC, etc.)

3. Count occurrences at the synset level: For each synset, collect count from the corpus.

4. Compute a probability for each synset, the probability (p(s)) is based on the frequency of synset divided by the total counts.

5. Compute Information Content: -log(p(s))

6. Turn IC into a similarity (or distance) score by using Resnik similarity, Lin similarity, etc.

**Why Information Content is excluding from the current evaluation:**

This metric measures semantic specificity and handles compound terms by decomposing into sub-concepts. However, it have to be excluded for now

""" ;
    dcat:keyword "Ontology Concept Matching"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "Metric"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "Classes"@en ;
    
    # Relationships and Provenance
    dpv:isApplicableFor <https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q184754> ;
    ftr:hasBenchmark <https://w3id.org/soel/benchmark/ALL> ;
    <http://semanticscience.org/resource/SIO_000234> <https://w3id.org/soel/test/InformationContent> ; # Has Implementation
    ftr:supportedBy <https://w3id.org/soel/> ;
    dqv:inDimension  "Ontology Engineering"^^xsd:string ;
    
    # Provenance
    dcterms:creator <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-9475-8159> ;
    dcat:contactPoint <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-9475-8159> ;
    dcterms:publisher <https://oeg.fi.upm.es> ;
    dcterms:publisher <https://ror.org/03n6nwv02> ;
    dcterms:license <http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .

